# --- Build outputs -----------------------------------------------------------
**/target/
**/Cargo.lock

# --- Node-local on-disk state (the ONE store + ext-UI serve dir) ------------
# Repo-anchored under .cc-app/, same posture as lb's own .lb-dev and
# rubix-ai's .rubix-ai/. Threaded into BootConfig at the binary boundary
# (docs/WORKFLOW-LB.md §3, CLAUDE.md rule 5). NEVER committed.
.cc-app/
.cargo/config.toml

# --- zig toolchain cache ----------------------------------------------------
# The .cargo/config.toml redirects ZIG_LOCAL_CACHE_DIR to a writable
# scratch dir because /home/user/.cache/zig is bind-mounted read-only
# on this sandbox box (zig fails with "unable to create compilation:
# ReadOnlyFileSystem" otherwise). Two flavours land:
#   1. The root-relative `zig-cache/` (the `relative = true` form of
#      ZIG_LOCAL_CACHE_DIR — cwd at compile time).
#   2. Any other zig cache the toolchain creates (e.g. inside rust/target/).
# Always git-ignored — never committed.
**/zig-cache/
/zig-cache/

# --- Tooling noise -----------------------------------------------------------
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/